reviews.review_text: Nice afternoon in SF As I understand it this show was way small and was for some record people and some fans. Harding was a small place and even in 71 the shows were getting bigger. I had a chance to see them in FE and Felt Forum in 71. This show is relaxed, except for Phil who always seems pissed off ! Anyway enjoy something you will never see again, but you can listen.
